{"title":"「网络流 24 题」负载平衡","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/331#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=331","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/331/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/331/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/331"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"G 公司有 $ n $ 个沿铁路运输线环形排列的仓库，每个仓库存储的货物数量不等。如何用最少搬运量可以使 $ n $ 个仓库的库存数量相同。搬运货物时，只能在相邻的仓库之间搬运。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"文件的第 $ 1 $ 行中有 $ 1 $ 个正整数 $ n $，表示有 $ n $ 个仓库。  \r\n第 $ 2 $ 行中有 $ n $ 个正整数，表示 $ n $ 个仓库的库存量。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出最少搬运量。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n5\r\n17 9 14 16 4\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n11\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$ 1 \\leq n \\leq 100 $"}]}